modName: Dark Brotherhood Door and Banners to Sith
summary: Dark Brotherhood door and banners re-textured to have the Sith symbol from Star Wars on them.
descriptionHtml: I re-textured the Dark Brotherhood Sanctuary door and banners to have the Sith symbols from Star Wars on them. The banners are an entirely new texture, while the door just has the Black Hand symbol changed. I hope you like it.
